<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//0f2f/0f2f109675a9ae110d5871b19f6a185a.com/large/19210004a0a2e273859a"></p> 
<p>仲春初四日，春色正中分。</p> 
<p>春分平分昼夜、寒暑，也预示着真正进入春季了，这时人体血液也正处于旺盛时期，激素水平也处于相对高峰期。膳食总的原则要禁忌大热、大寒的饮食，保持寒热均衡。</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//41c1/41c11b022b7ed5c57622fa40c9a08978.com/large/191f0004bf344af0d4bb"></p> 
<p>春分应该吃什么？搜索</p> 
<p>—肉类篇—</p> 
<p>春天天气干燥，应该多吃些滋阴润燥、少食动物脂肪类食物。</p> 
<p>宜大快朵颐：猪肉、牛肉、鸡肉</p> 
<p>—蔬菜篇—</p> 
<p>饮食应清温平淡，多食用一些益气补血、富含蛋白质的时蔬。</p> 
<p>宜大快朵颐：荠菜、油菜、香椿、山药、豆芽、莴笋、韭菜、春笋、木耳</p> 
<p>—水/干果篇—</p> 
<p>春天天气变化大，容易出现一些肠胃问题，需要选择一些滋阴清热，健脾强胃的时令水果</p> 
<p>宜大快朵颐：梨、桑葚、樱桃、草莓、菠萝、橙子</p> 
<p>时令菜谱如何做？搜索</p> 
<p>—早餐—</p> 
<p>香椿炒鸡蛋</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//6915/69157a18e6f2de0d2ff42f27f013f5ab.com/large/19210004a0a35f5b1571"></p> 
<p>by 秋天的蝎子</p> 
<p>配料:</p> 
<p>香椿3颗、鸡蛋4个、盐6克、油20毫升</p> 
<p>烹饪步骤:</p> 
<p>1.鸡蛋打散备用。</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//7f1e/7f1ed7625554ac1b864c4f76c87083e0.com/large/19200004d02120675574"></p> 
<p>2.香椿掰去老枝，洗干净备用。</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//478b/478b25645b6e168f740df9065049d5f9.com/large/191c0004d2c0aa5474dd"></p> 
<p>3.香椿切成碎末。</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//5f5e/5f5ee8eb8d6bc37ff2a098185ea55f0f.com/large/19210004a0a49615b822"></p> 
<p>4.香椿末加入打散的鸡蛋液里面。加盐。搅拌均匀。</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//7030/7030697f592801a2b11fec6acdf9f8cf.com/large/19190004c80ef88cc08a"></p> 
<p>5.锅热加油，中火两面金黄即可。</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//b9c1/b9c1272dbc8379cdb808c291aef702c2.com/large/19140006b12b1e07c78b"></p> 
<p>6.春天里的一道时令小菜。醇香美味。</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//0c02/0c02f30706c2966c1a4ac8a175748da4.com/large/191e0004cfc78da67d56"></p> 
<p>—午饭—</p> 
<p>春笋酿肉</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//fbf7/fbf7f57bc40375dcafdab35ce58b7088.com/large/19190004c80fec5e0a0a"></p> 
<p>by 拇指煮意</p> 
<p>配料:</p> 
<p>春笋7根、肉糜100克、葱若干、姜末少许、生抽少许、盐少许、鸡精少许、料酒少许</p> 
<p>烹饪步骤:</p> 
<p>1.春笋剥皮洗净，对半切开</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//143f/143fd0ebaaaa8b54c2bb0795572bf318.com/large/19200004d02326dd2b7c"></p> 
<p>2.上锅蒸25分钟左右</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//714d/714d28593c8c51a8cfa9dd19ac5ac6a9.com/large/19200004d024ad2ad4eb"></p> 
<p>3.蒸熟出锅沥干</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//b19a/b19af4ac448d3286672fe33f2739a58c.com/large/19140006b12ef3ffcec0"></p> 
<p>4.将事先准备好的肉糜填满笋心</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//b9b2/b9b21ad13d4892e4cb761cafa1f5087e.com/large/19140006b12ddf438cf9"></p> 
<p>5.上锅蒸15分钟</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//b096/b096db0b5595d9455c86a75edc417a7b.com/large/19190004c810aecee03d"></p> 
<p>6.蒸熟后撒上葱花淋上少许生抽即可</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//0b56/0b56144cf79ed78f58358adce35175bd.com/large/191f0004bf35ad31a785"></p> 
<p>7.装盘拍照</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//8662/8662e8668b2feba399193b55f59f58c9.com/large/19140006b12ccda36d7f"></p> 
<p>菜谱小贴士: </p> 
<p>1、正是吃春笋的季节，春笋要切去根部不嫩的部分</p> 
<p>2、肉糜可以调制的略微咸一些</p> 
<p>3、喜欢略咸口味的可以事先用盐码一下春笋 </p> 
<p>山药炖鸡</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//4556/4556a7676a95121eb63db1c09449284f.com/large/19200004d0258c345579"></p> 
<p>by 豌豆土豆</p> 
<p>配料:</p> 
<p>鸡小半只、山药二斤、油适量、盐适量、花椒十几颗、姜一小块、芹菜一棵、鸡精少许</p> 
<p>烹饪步骤:</p> 
<p>1.铁棍山药清洗干净，泡于冷水中。</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//a1e2/a1e2c71c543672645de4c8409e466239.com/large/19210004a0a5295f2537"></p> 
<p>2.取鸡肉一块，剁成大小均匀的块。剁成块儿的那张图忘了拍。</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//68e9/68e99d5e5757aec718d5f0f3e2b1f988.com/large/19200004d026c3a8c843"></p> 
<p>3.锅里放油，下花椒炸香。</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//4b88/4b88f1e986b369f3e577b71a6769281e.com/large/19190004c813cd2dbfa2"></p> 
<p>4.下入鸡块和几片姜，爆干鸡肉水分。</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//15da/15da939f5658ad52d4d43754728d4d92.com/large/19140006b13076443c3c"></p> 
<p>5.将爆香的鸡肉铲入炖锅内。再适当的拍一小块姜在锅里开火炖汤。</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//41ed/41ed34e1a6ace8a477114be7755069a0.com/large/191f0004bf36a22743a8"></p> 
<p>6.鸡肉炖个半小时左右，然后把山药切成片状。（我只切了两根山药下锅。）</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//afc8/afc8e1ced39be302273377e448ac3575.com/large/19200004d02b750c07c6"></p> 
<p>7.放入炖锅中和鸡一起炖二十分钟。开盖，加点盐鸡精调好味即可出锅。</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//5a2d/5a2dcb78bb9f4440935145380bb114b0.com/large/191f0004bf3778684eb4"></p> 
<p>8.放点芹菜叶在上面点缀一下就0K了。</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//d3c0/d3c06e2fb30257a1ad84f678d0989d9b.com/large/191f0004bf389b6f5b1f"></p> 
<p>—下午茶—</p> 
<p>自制樱桃糖水罐头</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//cf0d/cf0dd9aa0fa720149e7db3de2395d7f7.com/large/191e0004cfc9645288bc"></p> 
<p>by 虫工</p> 
<p>配料:</p> 
<p>樱桃200克、白糖20克、冰糖10克、纯净水500克</p> 
<p>烹饪步骤:</p> 
<p>1.准备樱桃</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//f290/f290f01c4036d68b74ef73d5c3835d95.com/large/19200004d027484c351b"></p> 
<p>2.去把去核</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//8888/88889e49bc220470c5464868b739aa58.com/large/19210004a0a79cf3233a"></p> 
<p>3.加白糖腌10分钟</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//92c1/92c1b666a4cecac2758d8ff5e3ddb193.com/large/19200004d029387f7b8b"></p> 
<p>4.锅中加纯净水和樱桃</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//c90a/c90ac9afba120034477cea1f6ccc69f4.com/large/19190004c812132de274"></p> 
<p>5.加冰糖</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//b1f1/b1f16139a090065c02aee694ff5da460.com/large/19190004c8142ad54dbd"></p> 
<p>6.开锅后稍凉盛杯</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//6675/667564e9cf937ff4640e6135ab06c423.com/large/19190004c81514c5d7ad"></p> 
<p>7.凉透可装罐头瓶放冰箱冷藏更好喝</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//d74a/d74a9425a4f9c5152429facd5553bc06.com/large/19200004d02ac404eb80"></p> 
<p>菜谱小贴士: 冰糖也可以换成蜂蜜。 </p> 
<p>—晚餐—</p> 
<p>花胶红枣炖鸡</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//1402/14020676ee6c657111e329b6a9730c75.com/large/191f0004bf3942019eba"></p> 
<p>by 独爱你</p> 
<p>配料:</p> 
<p>鸡腿一只、花胶20克、红枣6粒、清水适量</p> 
<p>烹饪步骤:</p> 
<p>1.鸡腿斩块洗净，红枣洗净备用，花胶洗净用清水浸泡六小时以上</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//ee57/ee57e966b9685e43189ce60258c54c21.com/large/19210004a0a9a8746785"></p> 
<p>2.把鸡腿、红枣、花胶放入炖盅中</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//1544/1544f4032b88fbc7425d493bb75551d1.com/large/191c0004d2c29094811e"></p> 
<p>3.加入适量的清水，没过食材即可</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//4445/44450c55545a85113d7d56c1da416622.com/large/19190004c816c26ba41a"></p> 
<p>4.盖上盖子，放入炖锅里，按“炖煮”3小时</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//1d21/1d2192b9e6f41e6de297238c91cf632a.com/large/191c0004d2c45270b50a"></p> 
<p>5.炖好盛出即可食用</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//843a/843aeaf12b7178cc985d4b0832df36c5.com/large/191e0004cfca4a7d1893"></p> 
<p>菠菜鸡蛋炖粉条</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//a11a/a11aaac05f8334ceaf4cc30ef0854e56.com/large/19140006b133716e5735"></p> 
<p>by MM_玫玫食材:</p> 
<p>配料:</p> 
<p>菠菜300克、鸡蛋2个、红薯粉丝1把、食盐适量、小葱2棵、鸡粉适量</p> 
<p>烹饪步骤:</p> 
<p>1.红薯粉丝放入冷水中浸泡10分钟。</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//11a2/11a24488ac5579d512ad3ecffdc4dd46.com/large/19140006b138d1171245"></p> 
<p>2.菠菜洗净切成大段。</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//4970/497026af6c21167dae8e14fa7b99b9be.com/large/191e0004cfcbea11287b"></p> 
<p>3.锅中放水烧开，放入菠菜焯烫后捞出控干水份。</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//80e9/80e9de7d8ecb771c5882fa26833b379d.com/large/191f0004bf3e434747e0"></p> 
<p>4.鸡蛋放入碗中打散，香葱切成末备用。</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//9be6/9be6af0acc9ede666d19f52e6e8163ca.com/large/19190004c818a0a0466c"></p> 
<p>5.锅中放油烧热，倒入打散的鸡蛋。</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//b109/b10999881a5edc550367ebbaae7d0bc0.com/large/19140006b13605231674"></p> 
<p>6.炒熟后用铲子摁成块盛出备用。</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//df66/df665a130a942c8db22d0bd40ab18a19.com/large/191c0004d2c7e5957b15"></p> 
<p>7.锅中放适量的油烧热，放入香葱末爆香。</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//2da4/2da49cbfe46e3bef72a9a0d2d4743a4b.com/large/19190004c81910d91581"></p> 
<p>8.曝香葱未后加适量的清汤或水。</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//0793/0793c04945c333ad5251d5eff34cf03f.com/large/19210004a0ab3c9785b2"></p> 
<p>9.烧沸后放入红薯粉条，烧至粉条透明没有硬芯。</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//2f63/2f630c1cacc427058262ffcf64ebf55b.com/large/19190004c81a2f76c14b"></p> 
<p>10.加入焯过水的菠菜和炒好的鸡蛋。</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//7972/7972bf3eaf9e5cc6e9b7434ac464fbec.com/large/191f0004bf3d23e2c643"></p> 
<p>11.中小火炖三两分钟，加入食盐和鸡粉即可关火盛出。</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//2e02/2e02dd9bba004935635aedf09bf06b47.com/large/19200004d02ca5aa0afe"></p>  
